{"tid":984020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下香港有冇地方賣鴉片？","createTime":"2019-01-16T12:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T04:52:57.000Z","uid":158145,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a785ec4ac791c55c3441b73b1a031787455daff7","tid":984020,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"我阿爺後生既時候有食開鴉片既習慣，由於香港之後禁售鴉片，令到賣鴉片嘅地方越來越少，由於阿爺搵唔到門路去買所以漸漸戒咗，依家佢差唔多過身，想喺臨死前回味下嗰種感覺，但係我上網搵唔到地方邊度有得賣，所以想問下大家知唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2b95197e557d6993c4a7252808259c38a3fcc4","tid":984020,"uid":94828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"你覺得喺條街會買到毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c8ea41757215251e620d2fa156a61d62cb1898","tid":984020,"uid":230890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d10b045a55bf5f67bcc25d59e6191ce73107f462","tid":984020,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"自己種啦"},{"pid":"618ee8dfd7dfaca3b21baba6a1b97391c07bfa0d","tid":984020,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T18:24:50.000Z","msg":"你去d 學茅山既地方求下人可能會比小小你既<br />\n但係犯法野唔好做喇"},{"pid":"134566f534a30ff983c5953045f359506c5110d8","tid":984020,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T18:28:04.000Z","msg":"自己開間福壽糕餅店<br />\n整幾件福壽糕比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab72f8eadd1dd231b3d44d0f86d94b7147316a7","tid":984020,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"以前九廣鐵路剛剛開辦 列車有一卡車廂專售同比人食鴉片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}